  '<h5>Creating innovative and iconic brands.</h5>\n\n<h4>We are a 360º branding agency born out of.</h4>\n\n<p>We believe brands are values in\n                                            motion.</p>\n\n<p>We work with iconic talent and iconic brands to bring exciting\n                                          concepts to market. We leverage opportunities to grow our client’s businesses\n                                          by designing new brand concepts.</p>\n\n<p>Whether it’s spearheading a cultural initiative through a compelling\n                                          call-to-action or realizing a client’s business objectives through brand\n                                          positioning and IP creation, our studio crafts branded narratives that unlock\n                                          communities and place discovery and affinity at the core.</p>\n\n<h6>Brand development to business development. We provide strategic design value to\n                                  grow products, corporate services, and retail brands.</h6>\n\n<h4>We create iconic, lasting, and emotionally driven brands.</h4>\n\n<h6>Ideate.</h6>\n\n<h6>Create.</h6>\n\n<h6>Launch.</h6>\n\n<p>We serve select clients starting from establishing initial DNA to\n                                          full expression of branding to launch.</p>\n\n<p>Strategic PositioningBrand\n                                          DNABrand\n                                          ArchitectureCategory\n                                          StrategyIP Creation</p>\n\n<p>NamingLogo\n                                                    DesignKey\n                                                    MessagingBrand\n                                                    VoiceVisual\n                                                    IDUX\n                                                    +\n                                                    UIPackaging\n                                                    SystemsStyle\n                                                    Guides</p>\n\n<p>Content\n                                                    StrategyBrand\n                                                    Art\n                                                    DirectionBranded\n                                                    CampaignsWebsite\n                                                    DesignApp\n                                                    DesignRetail\n                                                    DesignPackaging\n                                                    DesignSocial\n                                                    POV</p>\n\n<h4>We are brand-to-business experts.</h4>\n\n<h6>We have project expertise.</h6>\n\n<h6>We are culture native.</h6>\n\n<h6>We are ultimate collaborators.</h6>\n\n<p>We have executed all levels of branding projects, from initiating new\n                                          IP to helping brands resonate and reach audiences in new channels to create\n                                          meaningful growth.</p>\n\n<p>We understand the language and cultural cues of brands and businesses\n                                          that are pioneering success through influence - intersecting the power of\n                                          brands and talent.</p>\n\n<p>We exist in a business landscape where high-level creatives and\n                                          stakeholders are always at our table. We understand how to lead a\n                                          collaborative creative journey towards a unified brand vision.</p>\n\n<h6>Brand Studio is the creative engine behind Foundation partnerships and\n                                  corporate growth initiatives.</h6>\n\n<h4>We use an integrated mix of capabilities tailored to each project\n                                  to create the ideal studio model for our clients.</h4>\n\n<h6>Strategic Design.</h6>\n\n<h6>Strategic Brand Development.</h6>\n\n<p>Services for fee-based projects and retainers.</p>\n\n<p>Partnership in return for meaningful equity position.</p>',
